{"type": "article", "id": 18990, "title": "云石和青铜的咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-14T07:40:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143121V7me5ZLon4Qk3hsc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t智利的设计工作室 GT2P 联合纽约画廊 Friedman Benda 一起，推出了这张结合云石和青铜的咖啡桌，在迈阿密设计周上展出。云石作图案，镶嵌在青铜的桌面上，它们之间构成重和轻，复杂和单纯，不规则与规则的对比，很独特。此外，因为云石的自然纹路，所有的桌子都有独一无二的花纹。<a href=\"http://www.gt2p.com/Marble-vs-Bronze\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145709PmOpb5vrHxZaI1yA.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145709hw0PDlkxOiSNGacC.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261457107XY19RZEw5IiMFTy.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}